# Description of each variable:
# TOTAL_WALLETS: Number of wallets to generate (default: 10)
# TOTAL_TRANSACTIONS: Number of transactions to generate (default: 30)
# INITIAL_BALANCE: Initial balance for validator account (default: 5000)
# LOG_LEVEL: Logging level (debug, info, warn, error)
# LISTEN_ADDR: P2P network listen address
# GENESIS_TIMESTAMP: Timestamp for genesis block
# INITIAL_STAKE: Initial stake amount for consensus
# WALLETS_PATH: Path to store wallet data
# TRANSACTIONS_PATH: Path to store transaction data
# VALIDATOR_PRIVATE_KEY: Private key in hex format (without 0x prefix)
# DATA_DIR: Directory for storing blockchain data
# HTTP_PORT: Port for HTTP API server
# HARBOR_PORT: Port for Harbor RPC server
# HARBOR_SERVICE_ADDR: Harbor service address for node communication 